00:13:01.500 --> 00:13:03.579
I spent 12 hours a day with the guy on the fields.

00:13:04.759 --> 00:13:06.359
He even tried to teach me how to play guitar.

00:13:07.019 --> 00:13:08.219
He said it's a good way to impress women.

00:13:08.759 --> 00:13:11.319
Yeah, we're all a sucker for a guy with a sick string.

00:13:13.019 --> 00:13:14.239
